  "subject": "Add REG_TO_MSB as env param.",
  "commit_message": "Add REG_TO_MSB as env param.\n\nWhen deployed with OOM, should not register service to MSB by service itself. So add REG_TO_MSB as env param to control the function register to MSB when start service. Default value is True.\n\nChange-Id: If5133b1359636e962a6e4799f56c38c9364526a8\nIssue-ID: MSB-98\nSigned-off-by: LiZi <li.zi30@zte.com.cn>\n",
